Most times it is Better. But here it depends!... 
Here Disney who did Only the Dubbing had put some time and resources for a good dub. (some say en dub better than jap!) 
Also you can see that most of the time, the Eng dub syncs better than the Japanese original!.. 
Anyway, normally one doesn't watch this masterpiece just 1 time, but 10 or 20 times :) 
So you can watch in all Languages/Subtitles. The English script is slightly different from Japanese Original. There are notable differences. 
So It is recommended to watch this in Sub and then Dub also!.. :) 


